## 5. 실행 방법

### 5.1 robot-control 의존성 설치 및 빌드

```bash
sudo apt install libyaml-cpp-dev
sudo apt install libglfw3-dev
sudo apt install libeigen3-dev
```

MuJoCo 3.2.0 설치 예시:

```bash
wget https://github.com/google-deepmind/mujoco/releases/download/3.2.0/mujoco-3.2.0-linux-x86_64.tar.gz
tar xf mujoco-3.2.0-linux-x86_64.tar.gz
mkdir -p ~/.mujoco
mv mujoco-3.2.0 ~/.mujoco/mujoco-3.2.0
```

aarch64 예시:

```bash
wget https://github.com/google-deepmind/mujoco/releases/download/3.2.0/mujoco-3.2.0-linux-aarch64.tar.gz
tar xf mujoco-3.2.0-linux-aarch64.tar.gz
mkdir -p ~/.mujoco
mv mujoco-3.2.0 ~/.mujoco/mujoco-3.2.0
```

LibTorch 설치 예시:

```bash
wget https://download.pytorch.org/libtorch/cpu/libtorch-shared-with-deps-2.10.0%2Bcpu.zip
unzip libtorch-shared-with-deps-2.10.0+cpu.zip
sudo mv libtorch /opt/libtorch
```

`aarch64`에서는 배포 바이너리 대신 소스에서 직접 LibTorch를 빌드해야 할 수 있다.
예시 절차:

```bash
sudo apt update
sudo apt install -y \
  git cmake ninja-build build-essential \
  libopenblas-dev libomp-dev \
  python3 python3-pip

cd ~
git clone --recursive https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch.git
cd pytorch
git checkout v2.2.0
git submodule sync
git submodule update --init --recursive

mkdir -p build_libtorch
cd build_libtorch

export USE_CUDA=0
export BUILD_TEST=0
export USE_MKLDNN=1
export USE_DISTRIBUTED=0
export BUILD_PYTHON=0

cmake .. \
  -G Ninja \
  -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release \
  -DBUILD_SHARED_LIBS=ON \
  -DBUILD_PYTHON=OFF \
  -DUSE_CUDA=OFF \
  -DUSE_MKLDNN=ON \
  -DUSE_XNNPACK=ON \
  -DUSE_DISTRIBUTED=OFF \
  -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/opt/libtorch

cmake --build . --target install -- -j$(nproc)
```

빌드가 끝나면 `/opt/libtorch`를 `robot-control/CMakeLists.txt`의 `Torch_DIR` 경로와 맞춰 사용하면 된다.

`manif` 설치 예시:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/artivis/manif.git
cd manif
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
sudo make install
```

빌드:

```bash
cd /home/pms/robot_control/robot-control
mkdir -p build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ..
cmake --build . -- -j$(nproc)
```

실행 예시:

```bash
cd /home/pms/robot_control/robot-control
./build/robot_control
```

```bash
cd /home/pms/robot_control/robot-control
./build/robot_simul
```

